# 银河麒麟/Linux 交付项目统一使用 LF，避免 Windows 本机构建时混入 CRLF。
* text=auto eol=lf

*.sh text eol=lf
*.service text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.xml text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.go text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf

*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.wav binary
*.onnx binary
*.deb binary
*.zip binary
*.tar.gz binary

# 如果未来决定把大二进制纳入 GitHub LFS，可取消 .gitignore 中对应排除项后使用这些规则。
*.onnx filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.deb filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
